{"tid":642262,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"去家庭繁殖果d度買貓+新手疑問","createTime":"2018-04-25T15:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T03:42:55.000Z","uid":55523,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0503c271834869b7cdb45350ae6ba059fee336b","tid":642262,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"請問去家庭式生貓b的話有咩要注意？<br />\n已經上左去一次見隻貓雙親同呀嫲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻貓眼鼻無異常<br />\n所以想問係交收、比錢有咩要注意<br />\n同埋洗唔洗幾時帶佢去做body check？<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實買貓籠除左大細之外，仲有咩野要留意？<br />\n<br />\n我都支持領養既，但係當想要既貓係好難領養，咁就盡力揾有愛心既breeder，同埋堅持唔棄養啦"},{"pid":"462fc39bad45afcb2b299d8bc3e8402656f7ca81","tid":642262,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9363b01c52b03d0d53b0646af9a1461050fec233","tid":642262,"uid":136039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下係邊度搵既breeder?"},{"pid":"eb3b1917b63778e59be7d5bcfc12e7700714060e","tid":642262,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c7f48b6c66f77cfbdcdc6b5b0ee9ce6151a293","tid":642262,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"最後棄養就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6e9e483215a054bbb578130dd183acbc7dc2d0","tid":642262,"uid":1993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"你最後嗰句多撚餘<br />\n想講自己有愛心，但事實又做唔到<br />\n<br />\n直接講想買貓咪算囉<br />\n驚比人屌就唔好上連登問，實比人屌"},{"pid":"12c031fbb6627a1c6dc9685c0b032a0acf28ef7f","tid":642262,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"私人繁殖唔係有愛心breeder呀⋯⋯<br />\n正常breeder係有牌同會喺國際協會註冊如CFA<br />\n確保貓係純種，每隻出生貓仔都會同協會登記，有啲會驗埋遺傳病，生仔有限額唔會要隻貓一年生幾胎<br />\n所有賣出去嘅貓會絕育先賣<br />\n<br />\n即使喺呢個制度下都有老鼠屎，何況係無監管嘅私人繁殖"}]}